name: Ex4: Testing Sing Up, Sign Out, and Sign In again

steps.name: Press Give Allow Bluetooth button on welcome screen
Press Skip button on welcome screen
Press "Sign Up" button on welcome screen
Generate new mail box and fake email address
Click on "'samanthasoper@folllo.com'" field", clear and set app email for IOS or Android
Open link from fake email box for entry to the app
Set full app name in Name text field
Clean up and delete app after test
